Reference

Data

Use these functions to prepare or simulate choice data.

prepare()

Prepare empirical choice data

simulate()

Simulate choice data

summary(<RprobitB_data>)

Summary method for RprobitB_data

Model

Use these function to estimate a choice model.

fit()

Fit a (latent class) (mixed) (multinomial) probit model

transform()

Transform fitted RprobitB_model

Evaluation

Use these functions to evaluate your model.

summary(<RprobitB_model>)

Summary method for RprobitB_model

compare()

Compare RprobitB models

predict()

Title

plot(<RprobitB_model>)

Plot method for an RprobitB_model
